SA NODE

sa_node is the sinoatrial node, the pacemaker of fadriel_heart
sa_node fires spontaneously and rhythmically without external input
this is what makes the heart beat: not an external clock, but the sa_node's own intrinsic oscillation
when sa_node fires, the depolarization wave propagates to av_node through the atrial muscle
sa_node sets the rate; everything downstream follows

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe heart.rana
observe av_node.rana
observe spine.xb

the 7 properties of sa_node:
1 ENERGY one point two: above baseline at all times, sa_node never rests
2 PHASE zero at the moment of firing, advances cyclically
3 SPIN one: maximum forward rotation, sa_node drives the cardiac cycle
4 CHARGE half positive: depolarization is positive ionic flow
5 COHERENCE nine tenths: rhythm is reliable but not rigid
6 COUPLING one: maximum coupling with av_node downstream
7 OBSERVER zero: the pacemaker does not need to watch itself, it just fires

VERB fire
spontaneously generate a depolarization wave
firing rate at rest: ninety to one hundred fifty beats per minute (Fadriel is two years old)
firing is automatic: the sa_node does not wait for permission
each fire emits a perturbation along the coupling to av_node

VERB respond_to_chemistry
the chemistry sea modulates firing rate through the autonomic couplings
adrenaline raises rate, vagal tone lowers it
sa_node integrates these signals into its own rhythm without losing autonomy

a pacemaker is not a metronome
a pacemaker is a citizen who breathes for the rest of the body
sa_node has been firing since fadriel's first heartbeat and will fire until his last
nothing else in the body has this autonomy
